{
  "stem": "323.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That Jews lived together in ghettos, because they wanted to live there, and it was just a way of Jewish life.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was self-rule, no abuse, no hunger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then I found out that they weren't really ghettos.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, the Warsaw ghetto was a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was really also an extermination.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- we were given notices that we had to gather at such and such a place, and that you could bring a suitcase or whatever your belongings were and that you had 24 hours and leave everything else at home.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father worked till the end, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were the last-- there were three Jewish families that went on the last transport to Theresienstadt from Bielefeld.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the other Jewish family was a, a young-- a very young family with a little baby.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then other one was my father's secretary, who was really a single woman, who fell in love with a physician who had been married-- a Jewish man who had been married to a German.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he voluntarily went to Theresienstadt with us when we did go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And eventually, he had to lead a transport of children from Theresienstadt to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she volunteered to go along as his nurse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were both-- they all ended up in the gas chamber. 500 children plus the doctor and this woman, Anneliese.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they just-- that was the end of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we went?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was towards the end of the year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know the exact date.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] What was it like?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There were only the three families.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were put--we traveled in a regular railroad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't like any other travelers-- traveling after that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- we were allowed to take what we could carry.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
